trans-unit.source: Provides a type converter for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.LinkLabel.Link> objects.
Use the LinkConverter class to convert links of one type to another type, and to access standard values and subordinate properties.
Access this class through <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>.
